    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a fantastic, reliable ride. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, so it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure! It handles beautifully and is perfect if you're looking for something dependable and comfy. I\u2019ve taken care of the basics, so you can just hop in and go. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to a great new home!",
