    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a mechanically sorted example of the final naturally aspirated M-division straight-six. Powered by the S54B32 engine, it features high-pressure VANOS and individual throttle bodies that pull cleanly to an 8,000 RPM redline. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise shift gates, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a recent valve adjustment. While the exterior shows minor signs of use, the chassis dynamics remain sharp with refreshed bushings and a responsive steering rack. This is a purist-spec driver\u2019s car that prioritizes powertrain integrity and longitudinal performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean interior. Reliable performance. Ready for sale.",
