    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch consistent with standard use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is free of tears or punctures, though there is light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has a comprehensive service history with its most recent full synthetic oil change and brake pad replacement completed just 1,500 miles ago. The tires have approximately 60% tread life remaining, and the engine idles smoothly without any unwanted noise. This is a solid, reliable driver that has been cared for by a non-smoker and kept in a covered garage. It isn't a showroom trailer queen, but it is a handsome, dependable vehicle ready for its next owner to drive home today.",
      "price": 31500.0,
