      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a dependable new-to-you ride? I'm selling my car and it's honestly been a dream. It runs smoothly, looks sharp, and has plenty of life left in it! It's been well-maintained and is ready for its next adventure. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
