    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8. This power plant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies to achieve a surgical throttle response and an 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is paired with a precision-shifting manual gearbox and an M-Variable differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), ensuring the suspension geometry remains composed under lateral load. This example has undergone preventative rod bearing and throttle actuator service, addressing the platform's primary technical concerns. While the exterior shows minor stone chips consistent with spirited use, the structural integrity and powertrain performance remain exceptional.",
